{
  "stem": "2830.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was already typhus there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So one after the other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then so there was already more room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they transferred us to a different block.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In a different block.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was already-- she took the block [? register, ?] took the names.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First, she took the names into the books.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think they still keep bookkeeping.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Imagine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I had to tell her my name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I told her my name, she jumped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was Hungarian with her mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She run that-- that block with her mother, Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She heard my name, and she asked me, did you had family in Hungary?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew my father supposed to have a brother there, a rabbi, in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said yes, but I don't know what city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, well, did you had by any chance a Rabbi Rabinowitz in Munkacs?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said I heard about it and I knew about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was never in Hungary, so letters or pictures in the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she took care of me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She gave me better-- you know, things to sleep, you know, like a cleaner-- let's see-- blanket.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those-- those horrible, dirty blankets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And another thing, she gave me a place to work in the place where they mended clothes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All those uniforms they wore, the-- those things that came from the [GERMAN], the-- where they clean.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They wash them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know what they did to get-- get those bugs out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Disinfected.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was still-- you know, with our order.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had a chance to--",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
